headline: Japan NTT’s Data-Center Arm Plans Multibillion-Dollar Push on AI Demand
summary: The Japanese telecom giant’s data-center arm is aiming to pour billions into its business to meet rising demand for artificial-intelligence computing and other uses, its chief executive said.
